A cyberpunk-style digital illustration of a detective figure in a neon-lit server room, holding up a magnifying glass to examine glowing data streams flowing between towering black server racks. The streams appear as ribbons of electric blue and hot pink light, with visible packet-like segments traveling through them. The detective wears a long dark coat with circuit-pattern trim, face illuminated by the glow of the data. Holographic displays float nearby showing abstract waveforms and connection diagrams. The atmosphere is moody with dramatic shadows, rain-slicked reflective floors, and distant city lights visible through a window. Steam rises from floor vents, catching the neon glow. The overall mood suggests digital investigation and the unveiling of hidden network secrets.
